"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.3.5.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.3.5.1</span> 標題：供餅（consecrated bread, bread of the presence, showbread）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： לֶחֶם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lechem)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:23\">EXO 40:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:7\">1SA 21:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： לֶחֶם, פָּנֶה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lechem hapanim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:30\">EXO 25:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:13\">EXO 35:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:36\">EXO 39:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:7\">1SA 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:48\">1KI 7:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:19\">2CH 4:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： לֶחֶם, מַעֲרֶכֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lechem hama‘areketh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:32\">1CH 9:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:29\">1CH 23:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:34\">NEH 10:34</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： לֶחֶם, קֹדֶשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lechem qodesh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:5\">1SA 21:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:5\">1SA 21:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַעֲרֶכֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ma‘areketh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:16\">1CH 28:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:3\">2CH 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:18\">2CH 29:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַעֲרֶכֶת, לֶחֶם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ma‘areketh lechem)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:11\">2CH 13:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： פָּנֶה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： panim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:7\">NUM 4:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： קֹדֶשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： qodesh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:7\">1SA 21:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἄρτος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： artos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:51\">1MA 4:51</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἄρτος, πρόθεσις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： artoi tēs protheseōs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:4\">MAT 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:26\">MRK 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:4\">LUK 6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:3\">2MA 10:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： πρόθεσις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： prothesis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:22\">1MA 1:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： πρόθεσις, ἄρτος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： prothesis tōn artōn)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:2\">HEB 9:2</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>供餅是擺在上帝面前的供物，先是擺放在帳幕裡，後來擺放在聖殿裡。經文沒有說明餅的大小和形狀，但是從新約時期開始，在猶太文獻中有詳細的描述。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>英文“showbread”譯自一個希伯來文短語，短語的字面意思是「面的餅／臨在的餅」或「陳設的餅」。翻譯者不應試圖模仿這個英文術語。在有些語言中，這個詞被譯作「擺在上帝面前的餅」或「擺在上帝臨在中的餅」。還有譯本譯作「神聖的餅」（“sacred bread”，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ；“sacred loaves of bread”，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ），甚或「特殊的餅」（“special bread”； <abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:32\">1CH 9:32</a> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
